{
  "id": "69e2b092bbec7b967b934eb2",
  "title": "settings に関するやり取りのアーカイブ",
  "created": 1776464020,
  "updated": 1776464571,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69e2b092bbec7b967b934eb2",
      "text": "settings に関するやり取りのアーカイブ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464020,
      "updated": 1776464020
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0940000000000c3306f",
      "text": "[アーカイブ.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464020,
      "updated": 1776464023
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0980000000000c33071",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464024,
      "updated": 1776464024
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0980000000000c33072",
      "text": "[Settings] 内で生じたやり取りのログをアーカイブする。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464024,
      "updated": 1776464053
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0ae000000000070158a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464046,
      "updated": 1776464046
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b2af000000000011b090",
      "text": "from [Settings]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464559,
      "updated": 1776464559
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0ae000000000070158b",
      "text": "[/ [井戸端にダークテーマを導入したい]]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464046,
      "updated": 1776464089
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0940000000000c33070",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464020,
      "updated": 1776464020
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa79",
      "text": "from [Settings]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa7a",
      "text": "ログ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464567
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa7c",
      "text": " 2024-05-04",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa7d",
      "text": "  13:04:26 [CSSをbundle&minifyさせる]方針に戻した",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa7e",
      "text": "  \tminify、あまり効果がない気がします...[bsahd.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa7f",
      "text": "  \t\t転送時はどうせgzip圧縮するので",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa80",
      "text": "  \t\tminifyしない場合は開発中のコードだけインポートで、あとはbundle済みが使いやすいのでパフォーマンスが最適化されると思います。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa81",
      "text": "\t\t すみませんうまく読解できませんでした[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa82",
      "text": "\t\t  [\" minify、あまり効果がない気がします]が「minify有無が転送速度or合計読み込み時間に影響しない」と主張しているのはわかる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa83",
      "text": "\t\t  　合計読み込み時間：`Settings/style.css`およびそこからimportしている全てのCSSの読み込み時間の合計",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa84",
      "text": "\t\t  [\" minifyしない場合は開発中のコードだけインポート]が不明",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa85",
      "text": "\t\t   minifyしない場合=bundle&minifyしない場合？それともminifyせずbundleのみした場合？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa86",
      "text": "\t\t   \t後者です。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa87",
      "text": "\t\t   [\" 開発中のコードだけインポート]は[個々のCSSを直接import]のことかな",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa88",
      "text": "\t\t  [\" bundle済みが使いやすいのでパフォーマンスが最適化されると思います。]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa89",
      "text": "\t\t   パフォーマンスは合計読み込み時間のパフォーマンスのことだと推測",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa8a",
      "text": "\t\t   [個々のCSSを直接import]するよりbundleさせたものを読み込んだほうが合計読み込み時間が短くなるということを述べている？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa8b",
      "text": "\t\t    自分もそうだと思う[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa8c",
      "text": "\t\t    実際のところは計測しないとわからないけど",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa8d",
      "text": "\t    ただこれと[\" minify、あまり効果がない気がします]がどう結びつくのかがわからない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa8e",
      "text": "   やったこと",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa8f",
      "text": "    [settingsの置換を図るページの置換を図るページ]とSettingsにあったコードとを見つつ、取り込むCSSを選定した",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa90",
      "text": "    各UserCSSへのリンクの直下に、`@import`文を書く",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa91",
      "text": "    　以前はリンクとCSSが別々にまとまっていた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa92",
      "text": "    　各CSSのimport元へすぐ飛べるようにした",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa93",
      "text": "    一部の古い説明を削除",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa94",
      "text": "   新規追加",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa95",
      "text": "   　development modeを導入",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa96",
      "text": "   　 bundleせずにCSSを読み込む方式",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa97",
      "text": "   　今まで",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa98",
      "text": "   　 `style.css`に`@import \"./style_beforeBundle.css\";`を書くか、built codeを書くかで、test modeとproduction modeとを切り替えてた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa99",
      "text": "   　  コードブロック名を`style.css`にしたり別の名前にしたりして切り替えてた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa9a",
      "text": "   　変更後",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa9b",
      "text": "   　 `@import \"./style_beforeBundle.css\";`を`dev.css`に、built codeを`dist.css`に貼り付ける",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa9c",
      "text": "   　 `style.css`からは`dev.css`か`dist.css`のどちらかを読み込む",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa9d",
      "text": "   　 　コメントアウトで切り替える",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa9e",
      "text": "   　 `dev.css`にはdevelopment modeであることがわかるようなバナーを仕込んだ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aa9f",
      "text": "   　1段余計なimportが挟まるようになったので、若干遅くなるかもしれない[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aaa0",
      "text": "   　 気になるようであれば前のに戻して構いません",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aaa1",
      "text": " (2024/5/4 一日限り)[settingsの置換を図るページの置換を図るページ-bundled]のCSSを使う",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aaa2",
      "text": " (2024/5/1~)[settingsの置換を図るページの置換を図るページ]のCSSを使う",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aaa3",
      "text": " (2024/02/24~)[settingsの置換を図るページ]のCSSを使う",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aaa4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b0f9000000000081aaa5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464122,
      "updated": 1776464122
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b154000000000070158f",
      "text": "イベント",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464212,
      "updated": 1776464213
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1550000000000701590",
      "text": " [井戸端クリスマスモードUserCSS]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464213,
      "updated": 1776464213
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1550000000000701591",
      "text": "  code:style_beforeBundle.css.disabled(css)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464213,
      "updated": 1776464213
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1550000000000701592",
      "text": "   @import \"https://scrapbox.io/api/code/villagepump/井戸端クリスマスモードUserCSS/style.css\";",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464213,
      "updated": 1776464213
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1550000000000701593",
      "text": "  11月下旬～12月中にオンにする。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464213,
      "updated": 1776464213
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1550000000000701594",
      "text": "  2022-02-05",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464213,
      "updated": 1776464213
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1550000000000701595",
      "text": "   機能しないファイルが年中読み込まれるのもどうかと思ったのでクリスマスモード外しました[kuuote.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464213,
      "updated": 1776464213
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1550000000000701596",
      "text": "    それもそうか[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464213,
      "updated": 1776464213
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1550000000000701597",
      "text": "     大したコード量じゃないから放置してもいいかなとも思ったけど",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464213,
      "updated": 1776464213
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1550000000000701598",
      "text": "     CSSのperseに負荷がかかるから減らすに越したことはないのか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464213,
      "updated": 1776464213
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1550000000000701599",
      "text": "    11月の終わりに有効化すればいいかな",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464213,
      "updated": 1776464213
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b155000000000070159a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464213,
      "updated": 1776464213
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905ad",
      "text": "from [Settings]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905ae",
      "text": "切り出し作業中]多分終了した",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464571
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905b0",
      "text": " cf. [Settingsが重すぎる]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905b1",
      "text": " やっていること",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905b2",
      "text": "  UserCSSの機能ごとに適当なタイトルを付けて切り出す",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905b3",
      "text": "  \t一応、切り出し毎に[記法サンプル]で表示に不具合がないか確認するようにしている[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905b4",
      "text": "  \t[/icons/ありがと.icon][takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905b5",
      "text": "  切り出し先のCSSをimportする文を↓に書く",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905b6",
      "text": "  \t多いなぁ[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905b7",
      "text": "  \t1行だけのも結構あるし[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905b8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905b9",
      "text": "2022-02-11 20:41:51 [全角スペース]が入っていたのが原因で、[日章旗]以降の全てのUserCSSが無効になっていました[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905ba",
      "text": " code:diff",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905bb",
      "text": "  +@import \"../日章旗/style.css\"; /* 新規作成ボタンを置き換える */",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905bc",
      "text": "  -@import \"../日章旗/style.css\";　/* 新規作成ボタンを置き換える */",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905bd",
      "text": " 全角スペースが見えるようなフォントを使うといいのかも？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905be",
      "text": "  [Google Fonts]になんかないかな",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905bf",
      "text": "  なかった",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905c0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905c1",
      "text": "[** style.css直打ちコード]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905c2",
      "text": "最後の[@import]の次行以降に記述してください",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905c3",
      "text": "[Streamのフォントをレトロゲームみたくする]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905c4",
      "text": " 2021-09-27 なんとなく追加",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905c5",
      "text": " 2022-02-06 18:24:21 [Font Awesomeを常時使えるようにするUserCSS]に併せてfontを追加した",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905c6",
      "text": " 2022-03-15 12:02:22 performanceの問題がありそうなので外した",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905c7",
      "text": "  特に違いがなさそうなら戻すつもり",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905c8",
      "text": "  12:04:00 見違えるほど表示が速くなった[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905c9",
      "text": "  　いままで2回文字が消えていた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905ca",
      "text": "  　↓をはずしたら一発でrenderingされるようになった",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905cb",
      "text": "  　これ[ボトルネック]だったんだ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905cc",
      "text": "code:style_beforeBundle.css.disabled(css)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905cd",
      "text": " @import url(\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=DotGothic16\");",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905ce",
      "text": " .stream {",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905cf",
      "text": "  \tfont-family: 'DotGothic16', helvetica, arial, \"Font Awesome 5 Free\",\"Font Awesome 5 Brands\", \"AppIcons\", sans-serif;",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905d0",
      "text": " }",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905d1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905d2",
      "text": "Streamで背景色や画像が途切れないようにする",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905d3",
      "text": "code:style_beforeBundle.css",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905d4",
      "text": " .stream h1 {",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905d5",
      "text": "   background-color: transparent;",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905d6",
      "text": " }",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905d7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905d8",
      "text": "[mobile edit menu]を押せるように、[.expandable-menu]の長さを制限する",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905d9",
      "text": " `@media screen`は[scrapboxのトップページへのリンクをnav barに固定するUserCSS]に合わせた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905da",
      "text": " 　このUserCSSの設定、冗長すぎやしないか？[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905db",
      "text": " 　設定をシンプルにしたい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905dc",
      "text": "code:style_beforeBundle.css.disabled(css)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905dd",
      "text": " .expandable-menu {",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905de",
      "text": "   max-width: calc(100% - 186px); /* 126 + 60 */",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905df",
      "text": " }",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905e0",
      "text": " @media screen and (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 991px) {",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905e1",
      "text": "   .expandable-menu {",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905e2",
      "text": "     max-width: calc(100% - 201px); /* 126 + 60 + 15 */",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905e3",
      "text": "   }",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905e4",
      "text": " }",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905e5",
      "text": " @media screen and (min-width: 992px) and (max-width: 1260px) {",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905e6",
      "text": "   .expandable-menu {",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905e7",
      "text": "     max-width: calc(100% - 216px); /* 126 + 60  30 */",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905e8",
      "text": "   }",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905e9",
      "text": " }",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905ea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2b1cf00000000009905eb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776464335,
      "updated": 1776464335
    }
  ]
}